    "description": "<p>we believe that everyone deserves the opportunity to learn how to swim—regardless of age, background, or financial status. Swimming is more than just a skill; it's a life-saving ability, a path to confidence, and a gateway to fun, fitness, and freedom in the water.<br>\n<br>\nOur mission is simple:<br>\nTo make swimming lessons accessible, affordable, and inclusive for all.<br>\n<br>\nWe are committed to breaking down the barriers that prevent people from learning how to swim. Whether it's high costs, fear, or lack of access, we aim to provide solutions through low-cost programs, community partnerships, and a welcoming environment for beginners of all ages.</p>",
